-- Pemex Operations Not Affected by Quake in Mexico South
-- B y   C a r l o s   M a n u e l   R o d r i g u e z
-- 2012-04-02T18:58:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-02/pemex-operations-not-affected-by-quake-in-mexico-south-correct-.html
(Corrects to say south in headline)  Petroleos Mexicanos,  Latin America ’s
largest oil producer, was not affected by the 6.3-magnitude
earthquake that hit the country’s south today, the company said
in an e-mailed response to questions.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carlos Manuel Rodriguez in Mexico City at 
